data.title: Regional Educational Media Center (REMC)
data.text:
Kalamazoo Regional Educational Service Agency

Regional Educational Media Center 12 - Delivery Service

Important

REMC 12 vans will pick up educational items only. If you are sending several items to the same district, please box or bundle them with a rubber band.

Please ensure that all items have a complete mailing and return address. Items incorrectly addressed cannot be delivered.
